title: Mindfield (2012) TPB
description:
Collects issues #0-6. This is it - Century Comics' first full-color graphic novel featuring an all-new epic! When mankind's return to the Moon is thwarted by an unprovoked alien attack, astronaut Lucas Hunter and the covert organization known as Majestic suddenly find themselves on the front lines of Earth's defense. You're not so cordially invited to meet our new neighbors as Mark L. Haynes (writer of IDW's acclaimed 24 one-shots) and Khalid Iszard present the first graphic novel in this exciting science fiction adventure series.
